---
import "./Bath.css";
---
<section class="questions-bath">
    <div class="questions-bath__inner">
        <div class="questions-bath__intro">
            <div class="questions-bath__service">• WHY USE OUR SERVICE?</div>
            <h2 class="questions-bath__title">
                Frequently Asked Questions<br />
                About Bathroom Remodeling<br />
                in Maryland
            </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="questions-bath__desc">
            Planning a kitchen remodel in Maryland? You're not alone. We've answered the most common questions homeowners ask — from costs and permits to layouts and materials — so you can feel confident before starting your project.
        </div>
        <div class="questions-bath__faq-grid">
            <!-- Left Column -->
            <div class="questions-bath__faq-col">
                <div class="questions-bath__faq-item open">
                    <div class="questions-bath__faq-q">
                        How much does a bathroom remodel cost in Maryland?
                        <span class="questions-bath__faq-toggle">–</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="questions-bath__faq-a">
                        Most bathroom remodels in Maryland range from $8,000 to $25,000+, depending on size, materials, and customization. We provide clear, upfront quotes.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="questions-bath__faq-item open">
                    <div class="questions-bath__faq-q">
                        How long does a bathroom renovation take from start to finish?
                        <span class="questions-bath__faq-toggle">+</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="questions-bath__faq-item open">
                    <div class="questions-bath__faq-q">
                        Do I need a permit for a bathroom remodel in Maryland?
                        <span class="questions-bath__faq-toggle">+</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="questions-bath__faq-item open">
                    <div class="questions-bath__faq-q">
                        Can you remodel a small bathroom or half bath?
                        <span class="questions-bath__faq-toggle">+</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="questions-bath__faq-item open">
                    <div class="questions-bath__faq-q">
                        Do you offer aging-in-place or ADA-compliant bathroom upgrades?
                        <span class="questions-bath__faq-toggle">+</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Right Column -->
            <div class="questions-bath__faq-col">
                <div class="questions-bath__faq-item open">
                    <div class="questions-bath__faq-q">
                        What’s included in a full bathroom remodel?
                        <span class="questions-bath__faq-toggle">–</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="questions-bath__faq-a">
                        Absolutely. We specialize in open concept kitchen remodeling, including wall removal, space reconfiguration, and structural adjustments.
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="questions-bath__faq-item open">
                    <div class="questions-bath__faq-q">
                        Can I choose my own tiles, vanities, and finishes?
                        <span class="questions-bath__faq-toggle">+</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="questions-bath__faq-item open">
                    <div class="questions-bath__faq-q">
                        Is your bathroom remodeling work covered by a warranty?
                        <span class="questions-bath__faq-toggle">+</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="questions-bath__faq-item open">
                    <div class="questions-bath__faq-q">
                        Do you offer bathroom design help?
                        <span class="questions-bath__faq-toggle">+</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="questions-bath__faq-item open">
                    <div class="questions-bath__faq-q">
                        Do you offer financing or flexible payment plans?
                        <span class="questions-bath__faq-toggle">+</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>